Text:
Classification: Scripted
Genre: Comedy
Status: Returning Series
Network: BBC One ( United Kingdom)

Not Going Out follows the misadventures of a slacker named Lee. He hasn’t had much success in his life and usually performs various odd jobs to make a living, though he’s fortunate to have a kind landlady and friends who actually care about him. Lee has a lot of problems in his life, though through it all, he’s going to keep moving forward.
